00052 DomainBase *TREX::europa::details::trex_domain(EUROPA::Domain const &dom) {
00053   EUROPA::DataTypeId const &type(dom.getDataType());
00054   std::auto_ptr<DomainBase> result;
00055   
00056   if( type->isBool() ) {                                  // Boolean domain 
00057     if( dom.isSingleton() ) 
00058       result.reset(new BooleanDomain(0.0!=dom.getSingletonValue()));
00059     else 
00060       result.reset(new BooleanDomain());
00061   } else if( type->isNumeric() ) {                       // Interval domain
00062     EUROPA::edouble e_lb, e_ub;
00063     dom.getBounds(e_lb, e_ub);
00064 
00065     if( 1.0==type->minDelta() ) {                        // Integer domain
00066       EUROPA::eint i_lb(e_lb), i_ub(e_ub);
00067       IntegerDomain::bound  t_lb = IntegerDomain::minus_inf,
00068        t_ub = IntegerDomain::plus_inf;
00069 
00070       if( std::numeric_limits<EUROPA::eint>::minus_infinity()<i_lb )
00071        t_lb = EUROPA::cast_basis(i_lb);
00072       if( std::numeric_limits<EUROPA::eint>::infinity()>i_ub )
00073        t_ub = EUROPA::cast_basis(i_ub);
00074       result.reset(new IntegerDomain(t_lb, t_ub));
00075     } else {                                            // Float domain 
00076       FloatDomain::bound  t_lb = FloatDomain::minus_inf,
00077        t_ub = FloatDomain::plus_inf;
00078       if( std::numeric_limits<EUROPA::edouble>::minus_infinity()<e_lb )
00079        t_lb = EUROPA::cast_basis(e_lb);
00080       if( std::numeric_limits<EUROPA::edouble>::infinity()>e_ub )
00081        t_ub = EUROPA::cast_basis(e_ub);
00082       result.reset(new FloatDomain(t_lb, t_ub));
00083     }
00084   } else {
00085     std::list<EUROPA::edouble> values;
00086     
00087     if( type->isString() ) {                          // String domain
00088       std::auto_ptr<StringDomain> tmp(new StringDomain);
00089       dom.getValues(values);
00090       
00091       for(std::list<EUROPA::edouble>::const_iterator i=values.begin();
00092          values.end()!=i; ++i) 
00093        tmp->add(type->toString(*i));
00094       result.reset(tmp.release());
00095     } else if( type->isEntity() ) {
00096       std::auto_ptr<EuropaEntity> tmp(new EuropaEntity);
00097       dom.getValues(values);
00098       
00099       for(std::list<EUROPA::edouble>::const_iterator i=values.begin();
00100          values.end()!=i; ++i) 
00101        tmp->add(type->toString(*i));
00102       result.reset(tmp.release());
00103     } else if( type->isSymbolic() ) {
00104       std::auto_ptr<EnumDomain> tmp(new EnumDomain);
00105       dom.getValues(values);
00106       
00107       for(std::list<EUROPA::edouble>::const_iterator i=values.begin();
00108          values.end()!=i; ++i) 
00109        tmp->add(type->toString(*i));
00110       result.reset(tmp.release());
00111     } else 
00112       throw EuropaException("Don't know how to convert Europa type "+
00113                          type->getName().toString()+" to an equivalent TREX domain");
00114   }
00115   return result.release();
00116 }

00124 void details::europa_domain::visit(BasicEnumerated const *dom) {
00125   if( m_domain->isEnumerated() ) {
00126     std::list<EUROPA::edouble> values;
00127 
00128     for(size_t i=0; i<dom->getSize(); ++i) {
00129       EUROPA::edouble val = m_type->createValue(dom->getStringValue(i));
00130       
00131       if( m_domain->isMember(val) )
00132        values.push_back(val);
00133     }
00134     if( values.empty() )
00135       throw EmptyDomain(*dom, "Europa enumerated domain "+m_domain->toString()+
00136                      " became empty after conversion from TREX.");
00137     m_domain->empty();
00138     m_domain->insert(values);
00139   } else 
00140     throw DomainAccess(*dom, "Europa corresponding domain is not enumerated.");
00141 }

00143 void details::europa_domain::visit(BasicInterval const *dom) {
00144   if( m_domain->isInterval() ) {
00145     std::auto_ptr<EUROPA::Domain> tmp(m_domain->copy());
00146     std::string lo = dom->getStringLower(), hi = dom->getStringUpper();
00147     EUROPA::edouble elo = m_type->createValue(lo), ehi = m_type->createValue(hi);
00148 
00149     tmp->intersect(elo, ehi);
00150     if( tmp->empty() )
00151       throw EmptyDomain(*dom, "Europa interval domain "+m_domain->toString()+
00152                      " became empty after conversion from TREX.");
00153     m_domain->intersect(*tmp);
00154   } else 
00155     throw DomainAccess(*dom, "Europa corresponding domain is not an interval.");
00156 }

00158 void details::europa_domain::visit(DomainBase const *dom, bool) {
00159   TREX:utils::Symbol const &type = dom->getTypeName();
00160   if( EuropaProxyDomain::type_name==type ) {
00161     EuropaProxyDomain const &proxy = dynamic_cast<EuropaProxyDomain const &>(*dom);
00162     if( !m_domain->intersect(proxy.europaDomain()) )
00163       throw EmptyDomain(*dom, "Europa domain "+m_domain->toString()+
00164                      " became empty after conversion from TREX.");
00165   } else {
00166     throw DomainAccess(*dom, "Don't know how to convert domain "+type.str()+
00167                      " for Europa.");
00168   }
00169 }
